
**************************** Sorcerers' Guild News ****************************

Guild info files are now accesible via "more." Also, your saved charged will
no longer be lost when you renew. [3/26/93]

Should something go wrong with a spell, type "clear." to reset your magesoul.
[3/30/93]

You must now advance attributes in the gymnasium. You may have to raise int,
pie, and wil in more obscure locations at a later date. [4/8/93]

All guild command verbs will work with abbreviations. For instance "spells" may
be typed as "sp", "spe", "spell", etc. [4/9/93]

You can now use emotes with "tell". [4/11/93]

Share and Enjoy!

--Bastian

